LIRAGLUTIDE PROMOTES IMPROVEMENTS IN OBJECTIVE MEASURES OF 
COGNITIVE DYSFUNCTION IN INDIVIDUALS WITH MOOD DISORDERS: A PILOT, 
OPEN-LABELSTUDY. 
Authors: Rodrigo B. Mansur1,2*, Juhie Ahmed1, Danielle S. Cha1, Hanna Woldeyohannes1, 
Mehala Subramaniapillai1, Julie Lovshin3, Jung G. Lee1,4, Jae-Hon Lee1,5, Elisa Brietzke2, 
Eva Z. Reininghaus6, Kang Sim7, Maj Vinberg8, Natalie Rasgon9, Tomas Hajek10, Roger S. 
McIntyre1 
